globs: 
alwaysApply: false
---
1. Scripts must be simple bash scripts.
2. Use "#!/usr/bin/env bash" shebang.
3. Include only minimal error checking.
4. Limit user choices to y/n only.
5. Text should be limited to ASCII, no fancy icons.
6. Comment lines should wrap at 80, code lines at 120.
